    "# 03 Feature Engineering\n",
    "\n",
    "## What this stage does\n",
    "Aggregates topic vectors per business and per user to compute VADER sentiment scores, dominant vibe tags, K-Means persona clustering (k=6), and persona confidence/intent combo scores.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Input tables/files required\n",
    "- `lda_topic_results` (Table)\n",
    "- `merged_philly` (Temp View)\n",
    "\n",
    "## Output tables/files produced\n",
    "- `business_profiles`\n",
    "- `user_personas`\n",
    "\n",
    "## Key parameters to configure\n",
    "- `K_CLUSTERS`: 6\n",
    "\n",
    "## Expected runtime\n",
    "- ~20-30 minutes on Databricks."
   ]
